{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression","text":"NSExpression","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"symbolAvoidsEdges","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If this property is set to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":", symbols in this layer avoid crossing the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"edge of a tile. You should set this property to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":" if the backing vector"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"tiles don’t have enough padding to prevent collisions, or if this layer’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"symbolPlacement"},{"type":"text","text":" property is set to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolPlacement\/MLNSymbolPlacementPoint","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" but this layer is above a symbol"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer whose "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"symbolPlacement"},{"type":"text","text":" property is set to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolPlacement\/MLNSymbolPlacementPoint","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". You do not need to enable this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property to prevent clipped labels at tile boundaries."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The default value of this property is an expression that evaluates to ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". Set","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"this property to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" to reset it to the default value."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This attribute corresponds to the ","type":"text"},{"text":"symbol-avoid-edges","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"layout property in the MapLibre Style Spec.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can set this property to an expression containing any of the following:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Constant Boolean values","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Predefined functions, including mathematical and string operators","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Conditional expressions","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Variable assignments and references to assigned variables","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Step functions applied to the ","type":"text"},{"code":"$zoomLevel","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" variable","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This property does not support applying interpolation functions to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"$zoomLevel","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" variable or applying interpolation or step functions to feature","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"attributes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer"]]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"text":"Whether symbols in this layer avoid colliding with symbols in adjacent tiles.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"symbolAvoidsEdges","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"property","ex